{"tid":235574,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[假設可重遇] 香港一名球星宣布今季後掛靴","createTime":"2017-05-09T06:12:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-27T14:31:25.000Z","uid":9030,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"be0c993aadf5476a967a18c6c89b3155e55c21f2","tid":235574,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T06:12:56.000Z","msg":"亞冠盃　35歲鄭少偉季後掛靴 冀亞冠搏盡謝幕 <br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=dNeHxx%2FttK3%2FgpwSwFVImQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=1d3b9a16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】東方龍獅將於星期二（9日）晚香港時間6時半作客川崎前鋒，除了將會是這支港超代表於今季亞冠盃分組賽的最後一戰，亦極大機會成為「亨利」鄭少偉的告別戰，這位35歲前鋒於其個人fb透露將在季後退役。<br />\n35歲的「亨利」於2002年出道亮相港甲，效力過南華、傑志、天水圍飛馬及晨曦等大球會，並於2013年轉投東方，保持年年有盃捧傳統，惟隨東方龍獅今季四大皆空，向被視為「福將」的亨利亦要斷纜。東方龍獅主教練陳婉婷於賽前記招透露，或會在今仗末段時間陸續派遣副選上陣，意味「亨利」將有機會告別。"},{"pid":"6cbf0b052f93c5246aa164649619612353d82fc1","tid":235574,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T06:14:19.000Z","msg":"香港伊巴"},{"pid":"0767a6830adaa9bd525771fca134eab79476fad4","tid":235574,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T06:15:17.000Z","msg":"亨利可否不要老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6a1a794b5b94688f7041ffe6c07ba9a3c90a561","tid":235574,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T06:17:23.000Z","msg":"讓今天的我輕撫你<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/56rprp9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F56rprp9.jpg&h=73993f4d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/09/141707_9d835cd6232d91e9b8755ba3758474da.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F09%2F141707_9d835cd6232d91e9b8755ba3758474da.jpg&h=fe7d5c0c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"707ab42673a353137d5d5c1b7bfe2b9e0306a3ad","tid":235574,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T06:19:06.000Z","msg":"去邊隊都有冠軍<br />\n<br />\n雲加諗諗，簽返來掃地都好"},{"pid":"b5a372be34996625779550e4c7b38659cfb36a20","tid":235574,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T06:51:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去邊隊都有冠軍<br />\n<br />\n雲加諗諗，簽返來掃地都好</blockquote><br />\n今年一冇正式比賽冠軍就掛靴"},{"pid":"1f29810e5dab4960a182562c3c62a4e195b82935","tid":235574,"uid":35637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T06:52:32.000Z","msg":"打邊爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6793cf4a5eed6c448a92f05c93a0b4684870d3a1","tid":235574,"uid":96964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T07:00:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"692e14c0a8dadf3ae1d8d50d8a07944dda1cffd5","tid":235574,"uid":35189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T07:50:47.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"938e8c21e3d860c718a16588eea77e79971c666f","tid":235574,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T13:18:00.000Z","msg":"靴已掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfed552a2f4cfc9a40eb3543959c74370c4f2e36","tid":235574,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:10:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ao0w13vd\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fao0w13vd&h=83d8e276&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"40352621ab13f9b4534928fd2b9efd8685e0764e","tid":235574,"uid":21275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:21:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2d3a1c746b030108e5341caade1f184cca58d8c9","tid":235574,"uid":21275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:21:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4c8a21c050e2c1b7813826473717ab4b895750f4","tid":235574,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:32:14.000Z","msg":"35歲的亨利透露季前已有退役打算，考慮會先行進修，然後再回餽球圈:「十幾年都喺comfort zone，做球員喺球圈入面太離地，係時候出去撞下板，學習點去同人溝通。」過去有福將美譽的他幾乎季季捧盃，惟東方今季四大皆空，亨利也不禁笑言「數據係要嚟打破」，但亦不忘勉勵隊友收拾心情應付餘下的季後附加賽:「係有啲遺憾，不過唔係因為自己攞唔到盃，而係球隊一整季已經好盡力去爭取，嚟到季尾大家都好辛苦，今晚賽後有少少舒一口氣感覺。希望大家無論如何都要喺季後附加賽盡力而為，就算我未必有機會再次落場，我都好希望幫助球隊取得下季亞冠盃外圍賽資格，的而且確我哋係同亞洲列強有實力差距，但相信只要經過高水平賽事磨練，一定會慢慢收窄。」"},{"pid":"4e1114ddab44760f9b0267fe3cdb705e9f2a1280","tid":235574,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:34:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2aZVG5h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2aZVG5h.jpg&h=91eab05a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8f29b5daed41927ce832dff95562d906f403a99f","tid":235574,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T15:22:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Fiy94If2qZw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFiy94If2qZw&d=dNeHxx%2FttK3%2FgpwSwFVImQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=47be1bd0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Fiy94If2qZw</a>"},{"pid":"5577bef939afb109b239896518bfc076804d663d","tid":235574,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T16:03:24.000Z","msg":"退役後會先進修，但未來一定會重返香港球壇。"},{"pid":"4028e35ef53fa13f432c8af51da58a29fa5821a2","tid":235574,"uid":34490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T16:06:01.000Z","msg":"好似奧巴美揚"},{"pid":"0d37a23847ead89ae42f8c32408d8fde90eb8357","tid":235574,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T16:10:22.000Z","msg":"賽後訪問，亨利喊<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/EasternLongLionsFootball/videos/1071079129702199/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FEasternLongLionsFootball%2Fvideos%2F1071079129702199%2F&d=dNeHxx%2FttK3%2FgpwSwFVImQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=fd3cbac8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/EasternLongLionsFootball/videos/1071079129702199/</a>"},{"pid":"43f76d729c9646a0e4755fafe8d84518dc3bf2d4","tid":235574,"uid":103798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T16:13:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />8年前左右係修頓踢業餘冠軍盃賽，有個隊友搵左鄭少偉黎幫手，到換人既時候球證唔比佢出場，話佢係甲組球員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，最後我地12碼輸左個冠軍"},{"pid":"43de9a0869486d4c40a6caf2f0a2d08e3b7d1b66","tid":235574,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T16:18:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/danonthemove/videos/1946708092283124/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdanonthemove%2Fvideos%2F1946708092283124%2F&d=dNeHxx%2FttK3%2FgpwSwFVImQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=a2dbb23c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/danonthemove/videos/1946708092283124/</a>"},{"pid":"50e4faa72a57c23a1780e89303703c63b11bd6b0","tid":235574,"uid":30476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T16:23:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />8年前左右係修頓踢業餘冠軍盃賽，有個隊友搵左鄭少偉黎幫手，到換人既時候球證唔比佢出場，話佢係甲組球員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，最後我地12碼輸左個冠軍</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇錯係修咸頓睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"623aae9b8fd8004d0bfccb491f5b2b671af8bfd9","tid":235574,"uid":33657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T16:24:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />8年前左右係修頓踢業餘冠軍盃賽，有個隊友搵左鄭少偉黎幫手，到換人既時候球證唔比佢出場，話佢係甲組球員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，最後我地12碼輸左個冠軍</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇錯係修咸頓睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都睇咗修咸頓<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor